You're having so much fun.

1051
01:08:04,079 --> 01:08:05,440
I have my own chanting too.

1052
01:08:15,400 --> 01:08:16,680
Are you nuts?

1053
01:08:16,800 --> 01:08:18,439
Are we friends?

1054
01:08:18,960 --> 01:08:20,079
I'm your master.

1055
01:08:20,159 --> 01:08:21,439
Master is not my father.

1056
01:08:21,800 --> 01:08:23,720
Next time I'm going to muzzle you.

1057
01:08:24,279 --> 01:08:26,319
