1068
01:09:23,920 --> 01:09:25,720
Gecko, my ass! You idiot!

1069
01:09:25,880 --> 01:09:26,720
It's a bomb!

1070
01:09:26,840 --> 01:09:27,880
Bomb!

1071
01:09:31,399 --> 01:09:32,840
Boss, what do I do?

1072
01:09:32,920 --> 01:09:33,800
Boss!

1073
01:09:34,000 --> 01:09:35,479
Boss!

1074
01:09:38,119 --> 01:09:40,039
Dad!

1075
01:09:42,960 --> 01:09:44,880
My dad!

1076
01:09:45,000 --> 01:09:48,119
-How can they survive?
-It's not working.

1077
01:09:51,560 --> 01:09:54,600
You think it's not working?
Didn't you see?

1078
01:09:54,960 --> 01:09:56,800
It blew me up, idiot!

1079
01:10:18,600 --> 01:10:19,840
Ghost!

1080
01:10:28,279 --> 01:10:29,279
Em!

1081
01:10:41,960 --> 01:10:42,840
Ood!

1082
01:10:43,680 --> 01:10:44,600
I want to fart.

1083
01:10:51,000 --> 01:10:52,399
Hey!

1084
01:10:53,680 --> 01:10:55,800
They're those guys.

1085
01:10:55,960 --> 01:10:57,640
-The temple boys?
-Yeah.

1086
01:10:58,640 --> 01:11:00,239
I told you.

1087
01:11:00,960 --> 01:11:03,600
We're men. We're not afraid of ghosts.

1088
01:11:03,760 --> 01:11:05,199
Right?

1089
01:11:06,079 --> 01:11:07,359
Stop playing!

1090
01:11:07,760 --> 01:11:08,800
Why are you scared?

1091
01:11:09,199 --> 01:11:11,159
Our teacher's face is scarier than ghosts.

1092
01:11:12,079 --> 01:11:13,600
-Boo!
-Hey!

1093
01:11:14,039 --> 01:11:15,119
What are you doing?

1094
01:11:15,479 --> 01:11:17,279
Just kidding.

1095
01:11:26,880 --> 01:11:28,920
Headless ghost!

1096
01:11:30,399 --> 01:11:31,600
Headless ghost!

1097
01:11:31,800 --> 01:11:32,720
Teacher!

1098
01:11:40,800 --> 01:11:41,800
So cool!

1099
01:11:41,880 --> 01:11:44,239
They all ran away. They're scared of us.

1100
01:11:44,560 --> 01:11:45,560
Nailed it!

1101
01:11:47,039 --> 01:11:47,960
Clever plan!

1102
01:11:48,079 --> 01:11:50,239
-They ran away.
-Good job! I like it!

1103
01:11:51,199 --> 01:11:52,640
Em?

1104
01:11:53,159 --> 01:11:55,359
Do you smell a cigarette?

1105
01:11:55,600 --> 01:11:57,840
Who smokes in the temple?

1106
01:12:00,479 --> 01:12:02,920
Ood! It's a hairless ghost!

1107
01:12:03,520 --> 01:12:04,640
Did he shave?

1108
01:12:04,800 --> 01:12:07,039
Hairless my ass. That's a headless ghost!

1109
01:12:08,159 --> 01:12:09,760
How can you get inside?

1110
01:12:10,199 --> 01:12:11,680
Don't talk to him, dammit!

1111
01:12:11,880 --> 01:12:12,760
I'm not staying!

1112
01:12:25,399 --> 01:12:27,000
So scary! A headless ghost!

1113
01:12:27,279 --> 01:12:30,079
What kind of messed up ghost
will smoke cigarettes inside a temple?

1114
01:12:32,159 --> 01:12:33,960
What kinds of ghost do you want to see?

1115
01:12:34,239 --> 01:12:35,920
What kinds of ghost?

1116
01:12:36,439 --> 01:12:37,680
Lady Ta-khian?

1117
01:12:38,840 --> 01:12:40,760
I prefer Tani.

1118
01:12:42,000 --> 01:12:42,920
Lady Tani?

1119
01:12:44,600 --> 01:12:46,199
I know a chanting for Tani.

1120
01:12:47,359 --> 01:12:48,840
I call her for you.

1121
01:12:49,880 --> 01:12:52,840
Bananas withered at the tips

1122
01:12:53,279 --> 01:12:55,760
Gushing stream breaks them in halves

1123
01:12:56,039 --> 01:12:58,359
She carries them around

1124
01:12:58,560 --> 01:13:01,880
Bananas withered at the tips
Gushing stream break in halves

1125
01:13:01,960 --> 01:13:03,840
